column2: "respect,respect,respect,Did you feel that you were treated with respect and in a sensible manner at Wound Center?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Kände du att du blev bemött med respekt och på ett hänsynsfullt sätt på Sårcentrum?\")"

"involved,participation,involved,Did you feel involved in decisions about your care and treatment, as much as you wanted?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Kände du dig delaktig i beslut om din vård och behandling, så mycket som du önskade?\")"

"prompt.visit,availability,prompt visit time,Did you have a time for the doctor as soon as you wanted?,,c(\"Yes\", \"No\", \"I had no special request\"),-2,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Fick du en tid för läkarmötet så snart du önskade?\")"

"informed,knowledge,get informed,Did you get enough information about your wound / diagnosis?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Fick du tillräcklig information om ditt sår/diagnos?\")"

"confidence.physician,confidence,confidence in physician,Did you feel confident about the attending physician?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Kände du förtroende för den behandlande läkaren?\")"

"needs.clinic,effectiveness,needs fullfilment,Do you think your current healthcare needs have been met at the clinic via the tabletop?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Anser du att ditt aktuella behov av sjukvård blivit tillgodosett vid läkarmötet via surfplattan?\")"

"needs.drug,effectiveness,enough pain relief,Did you get enough pain relief for your wound when surfing the tablet?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Fick du tillräcklig smärtlindring för ditt sår vid uppföljningen via surfplattan?\")"

"satisfaction,satisfaction,satisfaction,How do you  appreciate the care / treatment you received at the clinic via the tabletop?,,c(\"Excellent\", \"Very Good\", \"Good\", \"So So\", \"Bad\"),-5,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Hur värderar du som helhet den vård/behandling som du fick vid läkarmötet via surfplattan?\")"

"safety.feeling,safety,feeling safe,Did you feel that the meeting via the tabletop felt safe and secure?,,c(\"Yes, completely\", \"Partially\", \"No\"),-3,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Upplevde du att mötet via surfplattan kändes tryggt och säkert?\")"

"use.intent,use,intent to use,Would you like to use tablet as an aid in your healthcare contact?,,c(\"Yes\", \"No\"),-2,attitude,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Kan du tänka dig att använda surfplatta som ett hjälpmedel i din kontakt med sjukvården igen?\")"

"time.length,distance.time,length of travel,How long do you need to go back and forth from your home to Wound Center?,,c(\"0-15 min\", \"15-30 min\", \"30-60 min\", \"60 min or more\"),4,time.length,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Hur lång tid behöver du för att ta dig till fram och tillbaka från din bostad till Sårcentrum?\")"

"distance.length,distance.time,distance of travel,How far is for you to go back and forth from your home to Wound Center?,,c(\"0-5 km\", \"5-10 km\", \"10-20 km\", \"20 km eller längre\"),4,distance,list(language = \"Swedish\", translation = \"Hur lång sträcka är det fram och tillbaka från din bostad till Sårcentrum?\")"
